1208.name: E AlSi 5
1208.Applications: Stick electrode for welding Aluminium alloys with maximum 2% alloying elements and for aluminium alloys containing up to 7% Si.
1208.Suitable_For: AlSi alloys with max. 7% Silicium, AlMg alloys with max. 3% Magnesium, 3.3206, 3.3210, 3.2315, 3.3211, 3.2371, 3.2341, 3.2151, AlMgSi 0.5, AlMgSi 0.7, AlMgSi 1, AlMg 1SiCu, G.AlSI 7 Mg, G.AlSI 5 Mg, G.AlSI 6 CU 4,
